                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18060219-58-defend607 t18060219-58-punish326"></join>
               Fined One Shilling
            </rs>, and discharged.</p>
               <p>Second Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Recorder.</p>
